title: Snowman Logo Card
description:
A custom holiday card with a fun snowman design. Printed on FSC® certified paper.
 
 Your logo or company name will be added to the front of the card in your choice of foil or ink. For foil, standard foil imprint charges will apply (and will be added to your order after it has been submitted). Click "Continue" below to select or create a verse and add personalization to the inside of your card.  After submitting your order, please email the logo that you want to appear on the front of your card to artdept@postycards.com.  You will receive a proof via email. As an added value when you order logo cards, you get:
 
 
 
  FREE Upgrade to Full Color Card Personalization (a $0.24 per card value) - add your logo or signature inside cards in color.  Select "Yes" for card personalization and select one of the color ink options at no extra charge.  Your cards will be discounted in the shopping cart. For foil, standard foil imprint charges will apply.
 
  FREE Artwork setup for the front of the card (a $25 value)
 
  FREE electronic proof (a $10 value)
 
  FREE extra envelopes - 26 white envelopes for every 25 cards ordered

description:
This small format desk calendar is narrow and spiral bound and features photographs of landmarks around the world. It is different than our original desk calendars as it features only 6 pages plus cover for possibly reduced postal rates.* Planning pages are not included.
 
 July through December pages are printed on the back of the January through June pages. When you turn the page from June, simply turn the calendar around and the rest of the year continues. Your imprint is on both sides of the calendar, so your name stays at the bottom of the current month.

description:
Your clients will enjoy the scenic wonder featured month after month in this handy desk calendar. The easel design puts the calendar and your name on your customer's desk all year long. Printed on FSC® certified, 30% recycled paper.
 
 Our Standard Deluxe Desk Calendar stays upright on any flat surface and is made with high quality twin loop binding so pages flip easily  The calendar features 13 months starting with a December 2014 bonus page. The calendar is 13 pages front and back plus the cover. Includes up to 6 lines of FREE imprinting (3 on each side, 30 characters per line).  Also includes FREE standard envelopes.
 
  
 
 Each month features a seasonally appropriate, beautifully photographed landscape and monthly planners on the back of each page allow room for notes.
